latestPosts.caption:
The whole drive-in experience and watching Dexter on my projector was nice, though I think that had more to do with the company.🥰

Not gonna mention what movie we watched but it was 🤢🤐

Here’s how much I actually spent on the outfit:

I think a cropped baby tee would’ve been ideal but it was impossible to find a cropped white baby tee that looked good with this. For all the regular hill road girlies yk how it is to find something that doesn’t have a print on it. I also added accessories because no outfit is truly my style without a butt load of accessories 😭

At this point I should just move to hill road 🤡

Now onto how much moniez I spent on the outfit
Vest: 500rs 
Tshirt: 200rs 
Skirt: 350rs 
Necklace: 50rs each 
Bangles: 400rs
Belt: 150rs
